Package: minionverse
Title: Easily Install and Load Minion Packages
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matthew James", "Henderson", , email = "matthew.james.henderson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: The 'minionverseverse' is selection of packages designed to be loaded
    in concert. The purpose of this package is to make it easy to install and 
    subsequently load those packages.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports: 
    cli (>= 1.0.0),
    crayon (>= 1.3.4),
    dplyr (>= 0.7.4),
    rminion,
    purrr (>= 0.2.4),
    rstudioapi (>= 0.7),
    tibble (>= 1.4.2),
    minionator,
    mopr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
